research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for New Berlin city, TX, include the Mayor and five City Council Aldermen. Information was primarily sourced from the City of New Berlin, Texas website. There was a minor discrepancy in one of the listed aldermen between the city's website and a municipal league directory; the city's website was prioritized for accuracy. No specific ward, district, or seat designations were provided for the council members, so they are listed without such designations.
